G1 Z1 F500;         ; Lower slightly - controlled movement
G1 X27 Y10 Z10 F500;     ; Move in paint - controlled movement
;G1 Z8 F500;         ; Raise brush - controlled movement
G1 F1200;           ; Set feed rate to 1000

